strapiEvent.name: DanceChance Season Showcase
strapiEvent.description: NWA Movement Hub presents the DanceChance Season Showcase on May 3rd and 4th at the Momentary’s RØDE House at 7pm. 12 local choreographers will present dance works of diverse genres in this two night program. The lineup is different each night so pick one or plan to come to both to enjoy the whole spectrum of ballet, contemporary dance, pacific island dance, jazz and tap, Latin dance, dance theater and more!
